title: Family Guy S01E02  - I never met the dead man
description: After taking Meg out for a driving lesson, Peter manages to smash the car into Quahog&#039;s TV transmitter, knocking out the entire town&#039;s reception. After first going through some intense withdrawal, Peter soon comes to enjoy living a life that doesn&#039;t revolve around the tube. His new high-activity lifestyle is wearing out the rest of the family, however, so they try to find a way to bring Peter back to the couch.
